column1: # Species: Sc = S. cerevisiae; Cg = C. glabrata
# Len_1: length of primary stress treatment
# Repl: replicate ID on the same day of experiment
# MM, PM, MO, PO: dilution rate corrected CFU values
# r: survival rate without the primary stress
# rp: survival rate with the primary stress
# low_count: whether the original CFU counts were lower than three
